    <header class="hero bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image:url(<%= asset_path 'home/background.jpg' %>)">
      <div class="md-col-8 sm-col-11 mx-auto">
        <h1 class="white h0 regular">Keep, cook, and share all your recipes with Noodles.</h1>
        <a class="btn bg-orange btn-lg mt2" onclick="_gs('event', 'Clicked hero button'); window.location='<%= sign_up_path %>'">Sign Up</a>
      </div>
    </header>
    <p class="lead sm-col-10 md-col-8 mx-auto px2 left-align mt3 mb2">Noodles is a simple library of all your recipes. It takes just a few clicks to add a recipe, and you'll never worry about finding one later. And Noodles is designed for the kitchen — cooking is hard enough as it is. No more folders of print-outs and scribbled notecards.</p>
