        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Share Recipes</h3>
        <p>Share favorites with friends with a quick link (they can save their own copies!), embed a recipe online, or even download a PDF.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/s/2rAW0DA" class="btn bg-blue">Check out a recipe</a></p>
      </section>
      <section class="sm-col-11 sm-block m1 md-col-4 bg-white rounded shadow p2 bs-bb">
        <div class="circle bg-orange shadow inline-block mx-auto" style="line-height: .9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="m1 fill-white"><path d="M8.1 13.34l2.83-2.83L3.91 3.5c-1.56 1.56-1.56 4.09 0 5.66l4.19 4.18zm6.78-1.81c1.53.71 3.68.21 5.27-1.38 1.91-1.91 2.28-4.65.81-6.12-1.46-1.46-4.2-1.1-6.12.81-1.59 1.59-2.09 3.74-1.38 5.27L3.7 19.87l1.41 1.41L12 14.41l6.88 6.88 1.41-1.41L13.41 13l1.47-1.47z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Cook Mode</h3>
        <p>In the kitchen, Cook Mode helps you out. It features big text, a minimal, focused interface, ingredient checklists, notes, and more.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/recipes/45/cook" class="btn bg-blue">Try Cook Mode</a></p>
      </section>
      <section class="sm-col-11 sm-block m1 md-col-3 bg-white rounded shadow py2 px3 bs-bb">
        <div class="circle bg-orange shadow inline-block mx-auto" style="line-height: .9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="m1 fill-white"><path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Collections</h3>
        <p>Organize your recipes into collections, which are groups of recipes. Then, share a collection with just a click.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/c/2A1J3Q" class="btn bg-blue">See a collection</a></p>
      </section>
    </article>
    <section class="mx-auto sm-col-10 md-col-8">
      <blockquote class="lead sm-col-9 mx-auto mt2">
        &ldquo;Whether you want to keep your own recipes or you need to jot a recipe you find online or on TV, this website is handy.&rdquo;
      </blockquote>
      <h1 class="regular mt2">Noodles is totally free. Try it out!</h1>
      <a class="btn bg-orange btn-lg inline-block mt1" onclick="_gs('event', 'Clicked hero button'); window.location='<%= sign_up_path %>'">Sign Up</a>
